target: USER.md

## Onboarding 必填项

> 本块由 template 管理, sync 时自动更新
> 用户个性化内容写在本块之外

```yaml
# === USER.md Onboarding必填项 ===
name: <您的称呼 (例: 佛罗多老爷)>
language: <中文 | English | mixed>
timezone: <Asia/Shanghai or IANA tz>
work_style: <think_more_practice_more | one_shot | iterate | collaborate>
field_limits:
  promotional_text: <170 | custom:100>
  description: <4000 | custom:2000>
  keywords: <100 | custom:80>
daily_report_time: <08:00 | custom:09:30>
block_threshold:
  app_store_reject: always_block
  private_data_leak: always_block
  workspace_pollution: block_if_recurring
  url_404: warn_only
comm_style: <concise_only | detailed_with_examples | show_code_blocks>
current_app: <VitaMindGo | other>
ios_team_id: <9L6N2ZF26B | your_team_id>
github_user: <lauer3912 | your_username>
bundle_id_prefix: <com.ggsheng. | your.prefix.>
```

###读取顺序

新会话开始时, Agent 应:
1. 读本节 (onboarding)
2. 读 `AGENTS.md` (人设/工作协议)
3. 读 `SOUL.md` (灵魂/语气)
4. 读 `MEMORY.md` (跨项目长期记忆)
5. 读 `IDENTITY.md` (我是谁)
6. 读 `docs/SOP-iOS-Local-Development.md` §0 (环境 onboarding)